{"tid":428818,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"安徒真係好垃圾","createTime":"2017-10-08T11:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T12:53:34.000Z","uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc3a095a561c824066b0ebca423d45d8b0644b5","tid":428818,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"筆名安徒的本土後殖理論「大師」羅永生，曾撰文狠批港獨思潮。他指中共不會怕港獨，暗指港獨運動為中國干預製造藉口。<br />\n<br />\n之後他更污衊港獨思潮，將之描述為香港公民社會受到侵蝕的病徵。<br />\n<br />\n可是他今天於《明報》撰文評論加泰隆尼亞獨立運動，卻盛讚加國的反抗歷史<br />\n<br />\n這不單是偽善，更反映其思維混亂、且完全脫離香港的現實，根本就是不入流。"},{"pid":"983ca41d23fbead26ae920088653a6cb783c0b75","tid":428818,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"羅永生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e633014331c71cd3d3a53245582c6cf88b966238","tid":428818,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/085818_6909cfb22e57878df40ce05acad8adcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F085818_6909cfb22e57878df40ce05acad8adcd.jpg&h=cf04ee2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6737a90fd5193782b7d0369be25c699454a52686","tid":428818,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/090731_a912a20f649a277c726b0cf76c67a993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F090731_a912a20f649a277c726b0cf76c67a993.jpg&h=d3306e3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c367cf089efd2acb09382b6d42929e0e2765cd1","tid":428818,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as